Cost-effectiveness evaluation of add-on dapagliflozin for heart failure with 
reduced ejection fraction from perspective of healthcare systems in Asia-Pacific 
region.

Liao CT(#)(1)(2)(3), Yang CT(#)(4), Toh HS(5)(6), Chang WT(3)(7), Chang 
HY(8)(9), Kuo FH(3), Lee MC(1)(10), Hua YM(10), Tang HJ(11), Strong C(1), Ou 
HT(12)(13).

Author information:
(1)Department of Public Health, College of Medicine, National Cheng Kung 
University, Tainan, Taiwan.
(2)Department of Electrical Engineering, Southern Taiwan University of Science 
and Technology, Tainan, Taiwan.
(3)Division of Cardiology, Department of Internal Medicine, Chi Mei Medical 
