(10)Department of Pharmacy, Chi Mei Medical Center, Tainan, Taiwan.
(11)Department of Nursing, Chang Gung University of Science and Technology, 
Chiayi, Taiwan.
(12)Institute of Clinical Pharmacy and Pharmaceutical Sciences, College of 
Medicine, National Cheng Kung University, Tainan, Taiwan. 
huangtz@mail.ncku.edu.tw.
(13)Department of Pharmacy, College of Medicine, National Cheng Kung University, 
