Mental health benefits of a 1-week intensive multimodal group program for 
adolescents with multiple adverse childhood experiences.

Roque-Lopez S(1), Llanez-Anaya E(2), Álvarez-López MJ(3), Everts M(1), Fernández 
D(4), Davidson RJ(5), Kaliman P(6).

Author information:
